originalText.text:
I am not the type to write reviews but HANDS DOWN to this place!!! My children loved their smoothies and I personally had the best coffee you could ask for. Must be because the cashier (very charismatic)  made sure she took our order to the detail for us to love our beverages, which made us feel truly special. They also a huge assorted amount of groceries.
Overall, this is fantastic place with great atmosphere to stop by if you are taking a walk in the afternoon by Central Park.
Will definitely be back!
